:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13575:"<p>Back at the WPEC Central, we often remind eachother &#8220;an e-Commerce plugin is NOT just a plugin&#8221;.  If you develop for WordPress and use WPEC or another Ecomm plugin, you know how true that statement is. Ecommerce plugins are big, bad and complicated &#8211; whether you&#8217;re a user or a developer.</p>\n<p>We&#8217;ve been yapping about the changes here at WPEC and you&#8217;ve seen some of those already in the releases over the past year, but by next year, WPEC will be a completely new plugin. While WP e-Commerce is the oldest and by far the most popular e-Comm plugin for WordPress (approaching 2 million downloads at this writing) we&#8217;re not deaf to the concerns users have expressed to us. We&#8217;ve been seriously examining and planning for both our users and developers and now we&#8217;re ready to start looping our developers in on what&#8217;s coming.</p>\n<h5>Resources for Developers</h5>\n<p>We&#8217;re consolidating our communication channels for developers and look forward to one solid base for communicating with you: getting feedback, announcing beta releases, and offering access to new featuresets.  Developing for WP e-Commerce is about to become easier and more lucrative than ever before.  Sign up below to get our first announcement this week, exploring the changes coming.</p>\n<hr />\n<form id="subForm" action="http://instinct.createsend.com/t/y/s/pjhkhy/" method="post">\n<div><label for="name">Name:</label><br />\n<input id="name" type="text" name="cm-name" /><br />\n<label for="pjhkhy-pjhkhy">Email:</label><br />\n<input id="pjhkhy-pjhkhy" type="text" name="cm-pjhkhy-pjhkhy" /><br />\n<label for="How do you use WP e-Comm?">How do you use WP e-Comm?:</label><br />\n<input id="cm478860" type="checkbox" name="cm-fo-uhilz" value="478860" /> <label for="cm478860">develop websites with WP e-Commerce</label><br />\n<input id="cm478861" type="checkbox" name="cm-fo-uhilz" value="478861" /> 