lements. Publish is a clean and minimal theme which puts you and your content on stage. Rundown is a grey-based responsive theme. [&hellip;]''>Weblog Tools Collection: WordPress Theme Releases for 11/5</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://ma.tt/2012/11/stallman-on-software-patents/'' title=''Let’s Limit the Effect of Software Patents, Since We Can’t Eliminate Them, by Richard Stallman, the founder of the Free Software movement (and WordCamp SF 2010 speaker). [&hellip;]''>Matt: Stallman on Software Patents</a></li></ul></div>', 'no');
